00:11:15.910 --> 00:11:20.430
with Sir Walter Scott's widely
popular novel Ivanhoe in 1820

00:11:20.430 --> 00:11:23.740
with Rebecca and her father
being among the lead characters,

00:11:23.740 --> 00:11:27.580
perhaps even paving the way
for the Israeli's ascendance

00:11:27.580 --> 00:11:30.620
as Prime Minister in
England in 1868,

00:11:30.620 --> 00:11:34.390
200 years after The
