00:11:34.390 --> 00:11:38.430
The Venetian Ghetto, where Jews had
to live, was constituted in 1516

00:11:38.430 --> 00:11:43.710
as you heard, only 14 years after
the Spanish Inquisition in 1492.

00:11:43.710 --> 00:11:47.290
Several very wealthy Sephardic
Jewish trading families fled

00:11:47.290 --> 00:11:50.880
to Venice, where Jews had been
allowed to live more freely

00:11:50.880 --> 00:11:52.920
in the Venetian Republic.

00:11:52.920 --> 00:11:56.090
There's little doubt that the
ghetto, with its strict boundaries,

00:11:56.090 --> 00:11:59.450
was a result of the Inquisition
fever sweeping the rounds

00:11:59.450 --> 00:12:01.540
of the Catholic Church.

00:12:01.540 --> 00:12:04.220
The Ghetto was divided
into two areas--

00:12:04.220 --> 00:12:06.570
the Ghetto Nuovo, the New Ghetto,

00:12:06.570 --> 00:12:10.260
and the adjacent Ghetto
Vecchio, the Old Ghetto.

00:12:10.260 --> 00:12:13.150
These names of the Ghetto
sections are misleading

00:12:13.150 --> 00:12:17.120
as actually the Ghetto
Nuovo is the older one.

00:12:17.120 --> 00:12:18.450
A large number of Jews

00:12:18.450 --> 00:12:21.660
from different backgrounds
came to live in the Ghetto.

00:12:21.660 --> 00:12:26.000
But over time they never developed
a distinct Venetian identity.

00:12:26.000 --> 00:12:31.120
Instead they continued strongly
to identify with their origins.

00:12:31.120 --> 00:12:35.400
Therefore, four of the five
synagogues were clearly divided

00:12:35.400 --> 00:12:40.320
according to ethnic identity in
the Ghetto-- the German Synagogue,

00:12:40.320 --> 00:12:44.540
the Italian Synagogue, the
Spanish and Portuguese Synagogue,

00:12:44.540 --> 00:12:46.900
and the Levantine Synagogue.

00:12:46.900 --> 00:12:49.830
There was a fifth synagogue,
the so-called Canton Synagogue,

00:12:49.830 --> 00:12:56.150
but that was built specifically
for private use by four families.

00:12:56.150 --> 00:13:01.950
The languages spoken at the time
in the Ghetto included Venetian,

00:13:01.950 --> 00:13:07.780
Italian, Judeo Spanish, Judeo
Arabic, Spanish, French and German,

00:13:07.780 --> 00:13:11.260
while Hebrew was traditionally
used on signage, inscriptions

00:13:11.260 --> 00:13:14.910
and for official purposes, as
well as wedding contracts and,

00:13:14.910 --> 00:13:17.330
of course, in religious services.

00:13:17.330 --> 00:13:21.400
Allow me, finally, a quick
background on the word "ghetto."

00:13:21.400 --> 00:13:24.310
Like with so much about the play
there are different explanations

00:13:24.310 --> 00:13:27.860
and theories about the
origins of the word.

00:13:27.860 --> 00:13:32.900
Some say the word originates
from the foundries in Venice,

00:13:32.900 --> 00:13:38.160
where the Italian word "getto"
is very similar to "ghetto."

00:13:38.160 --> 00:13:41.170
But it's most likely that
the word "ghetto" derives

00:13:41.170 --> 00:13:45.620
from the Gothic word
"gatto," which means street.

00:13:45.620 --> 00:13:51.140
And the reasoning for that is the
Jews throughout the Middle Ages

00:13:51.140 --> 00:13:56.480 position:56%
usually congregated along one street
where they would have all their Jew,

00:13:56.480 --> 00:14:00.230
all their shops and
places of commerce.

00:14:00.230 --> 00:14:04.110
So it was very easy to decide
to enclose a street like that,

00:14:04.110 --> 00:14:07.170
and put up boundaries,
and make it into a ghetto.

00:14:07.170 --> 00:14:11.200
The strict confinement of the
Jews and Venetian Ghetto ended

00:14:11.200 --> 00:14:15.000
with an edict by the
28-year-old Napoleon

00:14:15.000 --> 00:14:22.060 position:56%
in 1797 following his conquest and
dissolving of the Venetian Republic.

00:14:22.060 --> 00:14:24.090
That's what you need to know.

